<html>
	<head>
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
		<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	</head>

	<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
		<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-light" style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
		  <div class="container-fluid">
		  	<a class="navbar-brand" href="https://github.com/argovis"><img src="Argovis_logo-1.png" style="height:30px"/></a>
		  </div>
		</nav>

		<div class='container' style='padding: 0 10vw 0 10vw;'>
            <p>Your API key is:</p>
            <p><b style="font-family: monospace;" id="apiKey"><%= key %></b></p>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="copyToClipboard()">Copy to clipboard</button>
            <p id="copyStatus" style="color: green;"></p>
            <p>This is the only time we will show you this key; keep it secret, and keep it safe.</p>
            <p>Use this anywhere an Argovis API key or token is requested:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>In the API Key field when searching for data on <a href="https://argovis.colorado.edu">argovis.colorado.edu</a></li>
                <li>[python users] In the <span style="font-family: monospace;">apikey</span> argument to the <span style="font-family: monospace;">query</span> helper in <a href="https://pypi.org/project/argovisHelpers/">Argovis Helpers</a></li>
                <li>In the <span style="font-family: monospace;">x-argokey</span> request header for REST requests sent directly to the <a href="https://argovis.colorado.edu/apiintro">Argovis API</a></li>
            </ul>
		</div>

		<footer class="mt-auto">
		  <div class="text-center p-4" style="margin-top: 1em;">Â© 2025 Argovis</div>
		</footer>
	</body>

    <script>
        function copyToClipboard() {
          const key = document.getElementById('apiKey').innerText.trim();
          navigator.clipboard.writeText(key).then(() => {
            document.getElementById('copyStatus').textContent = "Copied!";
            setTimeout(() => {
              document.getElementById('copyStatus').textContent = "";
            }, 2000);
          }).catch(err => {
            console.error('Failed to copy:', err);
            document.getElementById('copyStatus').textContent = "Failed to copy.";
          });
        }
        </script>
</html>